Sentencas: Studies have been developed in last decades in order to produce NiO-based material to be used as anode in solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC).
Titulo: Study of NiO-GDC material produced by aqueous tape casting

Sentencas: Aqueous-based tape casting was used to produce NiO-GDC substrates with smooth and homogeneous surfaces and good flexibility.
Titulo: Study of NiO-GDC material produced by aqueous tape casting

Sentencas: Physical and mechanical properties were obtained in green tapes sintered at temperatures ranging from 1200 to 1400 degrees C.
Titulo: Study of NiO-GDC material produced by aqueous tape casting

Sentencas: The tapes sintered in 1400 degrees C showed the best density and porosity values and mechanical strength between 7 and 25 MPa.
Titulo: Study of NiO-GDC material produced by aqueous tape casting

Sentencas: SEM micrographs show a dense material with cracks and pores.
Titulo: Study of NiO-GDC material produced by aqueous tape casting

Sentencas: The sintered material shows the presence of nickel oxide and gadolinium cerium oxide.
Titulo: Study of NiO-GDC material produced by aqueous tape casting
